      • execAt

        public void execAt(long id,
                   SerializableConsumer<V> op)
        Execute the specified operation with the corresponding value of the specified id. If the entry is stored at local, the operation is executed sequaltially. If the entry is stored at a remote place, the operation is asynchronously executed at the place.
        Parameters:
        id - a Long type value.
        op - the operation.
